<?php
require_once 'ainaraVisionKit.php';

$client = new VisionClient('YOUR_API_KEY');
$result = $client->classifyImage('/path/to/photo.jpg');

print_r($result);
?>

For JavaScript, import VisionClient from ainaraVisionKit, create a client with your API key, then call classifyImage. Example:

